{"tid":1430691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"場運動嚟到今日，係時候分化！割蓆！","createTime":"2019-08-07T20:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T00:35:15.000Z","uid":43932,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3a4971325e9d20a568a39dc07a41acace63122","tid":1430691,"uid":43932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRGzm6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRGzm6p.png&h=8e27aca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳政府內部決以「設獨立調查委員會」作妥協方案<br />\n<br />\n［本報訊］<br />\n反送中示威浪潮由六月蔓延至今，已演變成多次暴動及街頭騷亂，一發不可收拾。<br />\n本報昨獲得一政府內部高層人士絕密爆料，指林鄭有感無力平息風波，卻明言「回應五大訴求係絕不可能。」建制派內部為保陣營，近日開始向林鄭獻計，指現在反對聲音已逐漸由反政府變成反警隊，故五大訴求中「成立獨立調查委員會」是最為快捷及可行方法平靜民憤，消息人士更指「張建宗之前道歉咪就係想試下水溫囉！」。故不排除林鄭政府將以「設獨立調查委員會」作籌碼，以追究警隊換回政府聲望。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>狂賀毅進狗就快俾人割出去！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6916f1ba208317b76bfccc8c1028b8b1b42f86","tid":1430691,"uid":275074,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以成立獨立調查委員會，我再不上街。"},{"pid":"64e6e448c3a0616cdd8fcd0b54e57eb05d4e6ed2","tid":1430691,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:56:43.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">曲</span></span>"},{"pid":"31158e937c680c913982058e9a86a7e0e3cfc860","tid":1430691,"uid":293066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:02:07.000Z","msg":"同時間, 張曉明又喺度4大理由放風喎"},{"pid":"7a09952de9197d81c64da8fe0b5235e7b0f7dbcd","tid":1430691,"uid":293066,"like":1,"dislike":